==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Treillage
<hw>Treil"lage</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>treillage</ets>. See <er>Trellis</er>.]</ety> <def>Latticework for
supporting vines, etc.; an espalier; a trellis.</def>
<rj><au>Spectator.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I shall plant the roses against my <qex>treillage</qex>
to-morrow.</q> <rj><qau>Walpole.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trek</ent>⟦br⟧
